reviewText: I bought this for my 7 year old daughter. She is a big fan of Austin & Ally. It didn't disappoint. I don't think she has taken it out of her DVD player since I gave it to her.
The shows are great and the dvd arrived only a day late but I love the show especially Ross Lynch I just wish Disney would put out season DVD's that way I could get all the shows.
This show is funny,  especially the earlier shows made.
My daughter LOVES the Disney channel and adores my find for her, Austin and Ally, that she can watch anytime she wants! No need to adhere to Disney's schedule!
I love this show! It's my favorite besides The Fosters and Switched at Birth. I'm devastated that it's coming to an end and this DVD helps me remember it!
Enjoyed it very much!  It's absolutely entertaining.
My Downs son is so excited over Austin and Alley, he has watched it four times already.
This is a great DVD! It has six of the best episodes of the series! Whoever compiled this did an excellent job!
great family fun.lovable cast and austin rocks.
Wish there were more episodes.  But still great dvd.
